head: Key
Type
Value
rows: (Required for all objects that are structural content items; PDF 1.3) The integer key of this object’s entry in the structural parent tree.

(Required for all content streams containing marked-content sequences that are structural content items; PDF 1.3) The integer key of this object’s entry in the structural parent tree. At most one of these two entries is present in a given object. An object may be either a content item in its entirety or a container for marked-content sequences that are content items, but not both.
